:chart: *Early metrics pull for internal release*
Hey all - As we launch AIHub for professionals, we are looking to be much more metrics driven, and today I wanted to start us on this journey. Here are early metrics from the internal release.

Thank you all for selfhosting and sharing your feedback. As we develop our metrics pipeline, we'll share more insights like this with all of you!

Please keep using aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com) and sharing your feedback in this channel!
